BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 125.52000000000001 610 Td (ADDICTION IS A FAMILY DISEASE) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 40 600 m 392 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 580 Td (When one person is addicted, EVERYONE in the family is affected.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 567 Td (You did not cause this. You cannot control it. You cannot cure it.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 554 Td (But you CAN heal from its effects on YOUR life.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 541 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 528 Td (HOW ADDICTION AFFECTS FAMILIES:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 515 Td (- Constant worry, fear, and hypervigilance) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 502 Td (- Walking on eggshells to avoid conflict) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 489 Td (- Financial strain from enabling or consequences) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 476 Td (- Broken trust and repeated disappointments) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 463 Td (- Isolation \(shame keeps you from telling others\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 450 Td (- Loss of identity \(your life revolves around them\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 437 Td (- Physical symptoms: insomnia, headaches, stomach issues) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 424 Td (- Children in the home absorb the chaos) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 411 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 398 Td (COMMON FAMILY ROLES:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 385 Td (- The Enabler: protects the addict from consequences) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 372 Td (- The Hero: tries to make everything look perfect) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 359 Td (- The Scapegoat: acts out to divert attention) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 346 Td (- The Lost Child: withdraws and becomes invisible) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 333 Td (- The Mascot: uses humor to diffuse tension) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 320 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 307 Td (Which role\(s\) do I play? _____________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 294 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 281 Td (THIS WORKBOOK WILL HELP YOU:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 268 Td (1. Understand what you CAN and CANNOT control) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 255 Td (2. Set boundaries that protect your well-being) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 242 Td (3. Practice detachment with love) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 229 Td (4. Build your own support system) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 8 Tf 40 216 Td (5. Begin your own healing journey) Tj ET

